room_title: Escape room "Fortune's Favor" by Escape Sacramento in Sacramento
room_description: Something has managed to steal all of the world’s good luck, leaving everyone else in misfortune! Find yourself and your team in an enchanted grotto near a sealed off cave. You’ll need to follow the clues left behind by a mysterious researcher to bring the good luck back to the world. Keep your wits about you! Nothing is as it seems here.
